General.Name: Pandox AB (publ)
General.Description: Pandox AB (publ), a hotel property company, engages in the ownership, operation, and leasing of hotel properties. The company operates through Property Management and Operator Activities segments. The Property Management segment improves and manages properties and provides premises for hotel operations, as well as other types of premises. The Operator Activities segment owns hotel properties and operates hotels. Pandox AB (publ) was incorporated in 1932 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
